room_title: Escape room "The Arcade" by Upside Down Escape Games in Taunton
room_description:
Welcome to the Upside Down Arcade, where players truly become a part of the game. You are there to celebrate your friend Darryl's birthday, but the birthday boy is nowhere to be found. He was definitely there a moment ago...
You've only got 60 minutes until Darryl's mom comes to pick him up from his party. Can you follow the clues your friend leaves behind to stay on his trail and discover his whereabouts? Or will your quest end in another "game over"?
